/*This problem is called Big Countries. It has been provided directly by Leetcode.

Information provided:
- Table: World
- Column names & Types:
	- name, varchar
    - continent, varchar
    - area, int
    - population, int
    - gdp, bigint
 - name is primary key
 - country is deemed big if it has an area of at least three million OR it has population of at least 25 million
 
 Guidelines:
 - Write a solution to find the name, population, and area of the big countries.
 - Return the result table in any order.
 */
 
 SELECT name, population, area
 FROM world
 WHERE area >= 3000000 OR population >= 25000000;

/* RESULTS:
- 6/6 test cases passed.
- Status: Accepted. */
